{"tid":2425662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亞視獨家直擊達哥病房親友道別 　網民鬧爆：醫院就咪影相","createTime":"2021-02-27T13:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T14:20:36.000Z","uid":271829,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"05a37cc04f9e7cea3dc43891370fc026e914fec1","tid":2425662,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T13:13:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fK2LVPIjZcnpxQ5idmKqeVJpHTo=/745x624/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PUSRH4JZQZBQLBYLLH5JN5EXSI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfK2LVPIjZcnpxQ5idmKqeVJpHTo%3D%2F745x624%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPUSRH4JZQZBQLBYLLH5JN5EXSI.JPG&h=b5d1229a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亞視竟偷拍達哥病房外情況，親友排隊入內見他最後一面。（FB截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zuUlWDYIFbkZsYShcgn_SpK45DE=/693x975/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FFGQ37AKDZERJGPB2LQHU7CJ74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzuUlWDYIFbkZsYShcgn_SpK45DE%3D%2F693x975%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFFGQ37AKDZERJGPB2LQHU7CJ74.jpg&h=5ca434af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亞視拍到達哥幼子吳韋侖進病房見他最後一面。（FB截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0ZCu1crrjyj2LYB3D7Y1AeGDwFk=/327x482/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IF4KHFR7YFAXJOVFSKCOJAYZWM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0ZCu1crrjyj2LYB3D7Y1AeGDwFk%3D%2F327x482%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIF4KHFR7YFAXJOVFSKCOJAYZWM.JPG&h=f5740777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網民不屑亞視宜擊房情況。（FB截圖）<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n亞視數碼媒體的FB今日都有直擊達哥病情，今午4時59分更貼出一條在病房外拍攝的片段，甚至強調「獨家直擊達哥病房，率先披露最新情況」，看到親友輪流入病房跟達哥道別，大家排隊進入見達哥，當中包括有首任太太和一對孖女、現任太太及兒子、關海山太太、駱應鈞夫婦、艾威和田雞等，戴着口罩出入病房的達哥孻仔吳韋侖一臉哀傷，身形高瘦的吳韋侖身邊有一名男親友陪伴。<br />\n<br />\n根據資料顯示，吳韋侖是達哥與大馬太太侯珊燕所生，年約18、19歲。亞視在這個時間仍進取的去偷拍病房門外情況，雖然拍得獨家畫面，不過此舉不尊重達哥及其家人，網民有見即留言鬧爆：「醫院就咪影相啦！」亞洲電視企業傳訊總監黃守東就指控回應：「亞洲電視人員今天到醫院探望吳孟達先生，並於得到其親友同意下，將病房外情況帶給公眾。亞洲電視並對吳孟達先生的離世感到難過及惋惜，並對吳先生家屬送上慰問。」<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210227/CE5S6IT46VF5NEI5WI5UTIUII4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210227%2FCE5S6IT46VF5NEI5WI5UTIUII4%2F&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm0yCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=fe289c65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210227%2FCE5S6IT46VF5NEI5WI5UTIUII4%2F&h=ba68aa63\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210227/CE5S6IT46VF5NEI5WI5UTIUII4/</a>"},{"pid":"d335d78b843e2e1d6273bf2e29d2405c784d1785","tid":2425662,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T13:14:38.000Z","msg":"rap"},{"pid":"89c5eda4922ab43c2c1db10a64ccf4d65d95988f","tid":2425662,"uid":164591,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T13:16:08.000Z","msg":"亞視係咪最中意搶住報人地死訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03cf80be73f99e33c918a7ff807108cdea743eb2","tid":2425662,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T13:26:05.000Z","msg":"支持atv wor"},{"pid":"3d3d044f8564474a29487cab730d32c5939c6ca3","tid":2425662,"uid":35393,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T13:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NGO0GRZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNGO0GRZ.jpg&h=91db78e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40c6e9099f5a5fb67b8e86938d8d521a531ccbb2","tid":2425662,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T13